Hello. Not looking to win this, but I really appericiate that @sgagsg posted this video. To those that find this context does not seems to fit the current situation, yea, this is because the video was made before April, prior to the CB. My intention was to raise awareness of what is going around the world at that point of time- Singaporeans still have the freedom to go out and meet friends, while many European countries were on lock down. And it really hit me that freedom/peace should not be taken for granted. And some of the COVID news/interviews really hit me in the feels. Hence, I felt it should be known, and if Singapore ever have to be in this situation (WHICH WE ARE IN NOW), we should really just cooperate and learn from other countries mistake (like social study like that la) and act what is right. Because once bitten, twice shy right? Thrice a fool?
(AND SIAN, CB KENA EXTENDED NOW). -
